-- A-Level Biology Flashcards (AQA, Edexcel A, Edexcel B, OCR A, OCR B)
-- Generated for the RAG Learning study app from existing notes HTML files.
-- One INSERT per topic. card_order restarts at 1 within each topic.
-- The 'level' column is assumed to already exist on the flashcards table.
-- Inline SVGs are used for diagrams where they materially aid understanding.


